
------------------------README----------------------------

here is the interface for the Double Regenerating Code

---------------------library infomation-------------------

0. autoconf-2.69
1. automake-1.14.1
2. yasm-1.2.0

above are needed to build isa-l 2.14.0
3. isa-l 2.14.0

----------------------------------------------------------

0. this directory is independent from hadoop-20 and can 
   make&run without build hadoop-20
1. drc.hh define the interface in detail, and those 
   functions will be called through JNI by hadoop
2. only support the one node corrupt
3. drc.cc to implement the interface
4. tester.cc to test the interface

to use:
  make
  ./tester

to clean:
  make clean
